column16: Aaron Judge flies out sharply to center fielder George Springer.
Jacoby Ellsbury grounds out, shortstop Carlos Correa to first baseman Yuli Gurriel.   Chris Carter scores.
Brett Gardner out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Josh Reddick.   Tyler Wade scores.    Chris Carter to 3rd.
Chris Carter doubles (5) on a line drive to left fielder Marwin Gonzalez.   Ronald Torreyes scores.    Tyler Wade to 3rd.
Tyler Wade walks.   Ronald Torreyes to 2nd.
